short_desc: If BIRTHSEX=2 then MENARCHE should not be blank in most cases
full_desc: If A1 Q5. BIRTHSEX (sex at birth)=2 (female) then Q7a. MENARCHE (age at first menstrual period?) should not be blank in most cases

short_desc: if ALCDRINKS in (4, 5) then ALCBINGE should not = 0
full_desc: If Q1g. ALCDRINKS (On a day when the participant drinks alcoholic beverages, how many standard drinks does the participant typically consume?) in (4, 5) (7-9 or 10+ drinks per day), then Q1h. ALCBINGE (In the past 12 months, how often did the participant have six or more drinks containing alcohol in one day?) should not = 0 (never)
